#include<iostream>
#include<queue>
using namespace std;
class func1
{
	public:
		
		int operator()(int a,int b)
		{
			if(a>b)return 1;
			return 0;
		}
		
};
class func2
{
	public:
		
		int  operator()(int a,int b)
		{
			if(a<b)return 1;
			return 0;
		}
		
};

int main()
{
	int N,op,x,y;
	priority_queue<int,vector<int>,func1> hi;
	priority_queue<int,vector<int>,func2> lo;
	
	scanf("%d",&N);
	int sz=0;
	while(N--)
	{
		scanf("%d",&op);
		
		if(op==2)
		{
			if(hi.empty())
			{
				printf("No reviews yet\n");
			}
			else
			{
				x=hi.top();
				printf("%d\n",x);
			}
		}
		else
		{
			scanf("%d",&x);
			
			sz++;
			
			if(sz/3==0)
			{
				lo.push(x);
			}
			else
			{
				if(hi.size()==sz/3)
				{
					y=hi.top();
					
					if(x>y)
					{
						hi.push(x);
						hi.pop();
						lo.push(y);
					}
					else
					{
						lo.push(x);
					}
				}
				else
				{
					lo.push(x);
					
					y=lo.top();
					
					lo.pop();
					
					hi.push(y);
				}
			}
			
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}
